Data load

LPS

Patir <- read.csv("~/Documents/MiGASti/Databases/Patir.txt", sep="")
names(Patir)[1] <- "symbol"

LPS

load("~/Documents/MiGASti/res_name_LPS2.Rdata")
res <- res_name_LPS2[!duplicated(res_name_LPS2$symbol), ]
rownames(res) <- res$symbol
EnhancedVolcano(res,
    lab = rownames(res),
    x = 'logFC',
    y = 'adj.P.Val')

EnhancedVolcano(res,
    lab = rownames(res),
    x = 'logFC',
    y = 'adj.P.Val',
    selectLab = c('IL6','CCL5','CSF3',
      'IL12B','IDO1','TNIP3','CXCL2','PTX3','GPAT3', 'CD9', 'ZNF331', 'ITGB5'),
    xlab = bquote(~Log[2]~ 'fold change'),
    pCutoff = 0.05,
    FCcutoff = 1.0,
    pointSize = 2.0,
    labSize = 3.0,
    legendPosition = 'right',
    legendLabSize = 6,
    legendIconSize = 2.0)

sign <- subset(res, adj.P.Val < 0.05)
sign_LF <- subset(sign, logFC > 0)
length(sign_LF$symbol)
## [1] 715
sign_LF <- subset(sign, logFC < 0)
length(sign_LF$symbol)
## [1] 5543
sign_LF <- subset(sign, logFC > 1)
length(sign_LF$symbol)
## [1] 78
sign_LF <- subset(sign, logFC < -1)
length(sign_LF$symbol)
## [1] 45
